### Create Audio Recording Using createAsync with High Quality Preset

Source: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/public/llms-sdk-v53.0.0.txt

Asynchronously creates and starts an audio recording using the `Audio.Recording.createAsync` method with the `HIGH_QUALITY` preset. Wrap the call in a try-catch block to handle potential errors during recording setup.

```javascript
try {   const { recording: recordingObject, status } = await Audio.Recording.createAsync(
     Audio.RecordingOptionsPresets.HIGH_QUALITY
   );
   // You are now recording!
 } catch (error) {
   // An error occurred!
 }
```

